w.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%A0%E5%91%8A%E8%A8%B4%E6%88%91%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%94%A8-%E9%82%A3%E9%BA%BC%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E5%91%A2/ |title=是你告訴我和平示威沒有用，那麼文明投票呢？ |publisher=立場新聞 |date=2019-11-26 |accessdate=2020-01-11 |archive-date=2021-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624024113/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%A0%E5%91%8A%E8%A8%B4%E6%88%91%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%94%A8-%E9%82%A3%E9%BA%BC%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E5%91%A2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20191126/00176_036.html |title=2019年區議選舉結果：泛民167萬票VS建制120萬票 |publisher=東方日報 |date=2019-11-25 |accessdate=2020-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215133256/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20191126/00176_036.html |archive-date=2019-12-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-11/26/37910.html |title=鮑勃:區議會選舉之後的政治走向 |access-date=2020-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200113092659/https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-11/26/37910.html |archive-date=2020-01-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{NoteTag|依照不同媒體的統計，差距大概在30多萬至40多萬之間，各方說法不一。}}。

